FOR ELLA AND SATHVIKA

1. windows --> Administrative Tools --> Computer Management --> Local Users and Groups
 - Disable the Built-In Accounts --> Click on it and check off Disable account
 - Right Click on the User --> Set Password and set 'everyone' the same password
 - Check of 'Member Of'

2. Updating:
 - Go to README --> Click on the three dashes on the top --> Help --> About Firefox --> Update
 - Same for everything ^

3. Windows --> User Account Control --> Set High --> click 'okay'

4. Windows --> Check Firewall Status --> Use Recommended Settings 

5. Windows --> Add or Remove Programs --> Delete NMap, Npcap, 

6. Windows --> Services --> Delete Microsoft FTP Service --> Right Click --> Properties --> Stop and STARTUP TYPE (DISABLED) --> Apply
